      "heading": "",
      "text": "UniFi® Access Card is a highly secure NFC smart card compatible with the UniFi Access system."
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UA-Card is a pack of 10 highly secure NFC (Near Field Communication) access cards designed to work seamlessly with the UniFi Access system. Each card incorporates advanced security features, including AES-128 encryption and the UniFi Access Proprietary Security Protocol, ensuring the protection of card data from leaks and unauthorized duplication. These contactless NFC cards are specifically engineered to provide secure access control, making them ideal for distribution to employees and guests within a controlled environment. The integration of these security measures guarantees that each card remains secure and is safeguarded against potential security threats, thereby maintaining the integrity of the access control system they are part of"
    }
